{"tid":1503024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香城Online 職業整合與戰術討論","createTime":"2019-08-24T19:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T23:22:34.000Z","uid":3722,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3f575a61ea6590bfa9c17a6ac080f848b1524944","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:37:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8cEjK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8cEjK2.png&h=095679c1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n首先好對唔住我騎劫咗叔叔Ｃ嘅香城Ｏｎｌｉｎｅ　ｐｏｓｔ，原ｐｏ喺呢度。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［每天更新 人手置頂]7.21 香城Online終極裝備手冊+懶人包（有App)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331713</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［快入幫手！］正版香城Online玩家交流區！要你幫忙更新系統！ ！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382217</a></span><br />\n<br />\n小弟都係新手，玩咗幾個禮拜香城Online 想同大家簡略整合下隻Game 入面有咩職業，咁大家可以因應返自己能力同取向㨂返啱自己嘅嘢嚟玩。<br />\n<br />\n目錄<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n＃０２&mdash;７，職業導覧<br />\n ＃０２裝修佬、商人<br />\n ＃０３弓箭手<br />\n ＃０４長矛兵、棍盾兵<br />\n ＃０５哨兵、咪手／旗手<br />\n ＃０６工兵、工廠兵<br />\n ＃０７急救員、滅火隊<br />\n<br />\n＃０８，戰術討論<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以上純屬學術研究交流。<br />\n只供遊戲用途，並不誘使或鼓吹任何行動。<br />\n若使用本頁資訊導致任何（法律）問題，本頁及相關人士恕不負責。</span>"},{"pid":"1c5726dcda64aa7d214494a1111054da597e7d10","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:37:19.000Z","msg":"職業難度分級：<br />\n白色：入門<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">淺藍色</span>：要小心<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">金色</span>：保持警惕<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>：時刻保持自身安全<br />\n當然，唔係淺藍色金色就可以鬆懈，每個職業都有佢危險之處，安全打機，出入平安。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqCH2ps.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqCH2ps.png&h=2f7192c8&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>裝修佬</strong></span><br />\n首先ＧＭ都有講過，一開ＧＡＭＥ最好㨂做裝修佬，然後再轉其他職。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩用：<br />\n做裝修佬先解鎖到基本防具。唔係裝修佬而又有裝嘅話會畀ＧＭ當開外掛收裝ban AC。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">雖然係裝修佬都有機會畀ＧＭ收裝ＣＬＳ</span></span><br />\n要點做：<br />\n裝修佬呢個職業㨂職都要課金，百令二百個金幣。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkmanpower.com/safety_card.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmanpower.com%2Fsafety_card.php&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=824a29c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkmanpower.com/safety_card.php</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.emhk.org/zh-hk/course_detail.html?id=995de9e4-4088-4a19-a32a-4220884df26e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.emhk.org%2Fzh-hk%2Fcourse_detail.html%3Fid%3D995de9e4-4088-4a19-a32a-4220884df26e&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=74a0165a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.emhk.org/zh-hk/course_detail.html?id=995de9e4-4088-4a19-a32a-4220884df26e</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8RxFc3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8RxFc3.png&h=c6b95066&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">商人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n商人負責喺唔同渠道課金，買裝畀前線嘅玩家。要知道唔係個個玩家都有能力重課。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要點做：<br />\n應付到課金，呢隻ＧＡＭＥ課金唔平。<br />\n喺唔同嘅ＴＧ谷都有唔同嘅商會畀商人交流應該買啲咩，同埋買完之後要點做。呢一點小弟唔多清楚，知道嘅手足可以喺下面補充。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Go0PaF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Go0PaF.png&h=a8fa614c&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">物資兵</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n將商人用血汗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />課金買嘅裝備送上前線。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n喺唔同嘅ＴＧ谷商會入面同商人保持聯絡。<br />\n如果物資量多嘅話可能要有車先送到啲物資入副本，然後再喺副本地圖入面同其他物資兵一齊派畀其他玩家。"},{"pid":"dbe2b76725d900434bd3a382ab816472c236cc71","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VTGE4Mw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVTGE4Mw.png&h=356dd443&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>弓箭手</strong></span></span><br />\n弓箭手除咗可以喺遠距離打怪之外，當弓箭手數量多而齊射嘅時候，可以對啲怪做到火力壓制嘅效果。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n主要都係火力壓制啲怪，令到佢哋開遠攻技能嘅難度增加，減少近攻隊友所受到嘅攻擊。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n首先你要有夠好嘅眼界，確保到唔會ＴＫ到隊友先。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">漆彈</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/CEF806n.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEF806n.png&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=c8ce51b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/CEF806n.png</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[721] 彩彈戰術，實測報告<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325862</a></span><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 就算打中隊友都唔會受傷，只要洗就冇影響。<br />\n- 只要打中啲怪，因為要維持封鎖線，所以佢地係冇得洗（或唔夠水洗），亦都可以減低佢地人手調動嘅靈活性以及阻止包圍網形成。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 需要海量油漆以隨時應對不同情況。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">古代Ｍ巾</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/z8jrKR6.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8jrKR6.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=58bb158a\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/z8jrKR6.jpg</a><br />\n教學：o6kdRs4x1fs<br />\n優點：<br />\n- 好易整。<br />\n- 掉乜都得。<br />\n- 高攻。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 難，但係又唔係話冇可能嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>童年玩兒</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/A8THie0.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8THie0.png&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=23420627\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/A8THie0.png</a><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 易用。<br />\n- 平。<br />\n- 就算想自己整都唔難。<br />\n- 好多嘢都射得（任何球狀物體、電芯）。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 應該要去外國商城先有得買，送貨須時。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHB9HKR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHB9HKR.png&h=92295968&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>砲兵團</strong></span></span><br />\n鐘意玩遠程攻擊又鐘意團隊合作嘅玩家，可以做砲兵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n對啲怪做火力壓制，打怪嘅陣地就可以加到隊友士氣。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n組一個二至四人嘅小隊（一至兩個人企喺度，一個發射，一個幫手上彈（Optional））。<br />\n同隊友有好嘅合作。<br />\n負責發射嘅手足要有好嘅眼界。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>友誼萬歲</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/RdkFPvf.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRdkFPvf.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=0cf4f395\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/RdkFPvf.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://amzn.to/2Zo3Xp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2Zo3Xp4&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=4ddd447b\" target=\"_blank\">https://amzn.to/2Zo3Xp4</a><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 平。<br />\n- 要自己整都唔係好難，做尖嗰啲阻力帶都可以用嚟改裝。<br />\n- 承上，自己整嘅仲可以自己較磅數。<br />\n- 易收藏。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 要有隊友，不過開聲問句，點都有人同你組隊嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7404f4f9ecd09302545462bbb80b86b8e24939c","tid":1503024,"uid":110509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:38:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月1 一定係機場<br />\n之後每個星期六/日 要有一日一定係機場</span></span>"},{"pid":"d28e865a42e43aff8fc3a935ddd7b4ab8180a68a","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/swpjkJ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FswpjkJ4.png&h=8ca73455&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>長矛兵</strong></span></span><br />\n有心理準備同有意志近戰打怪嘅玩家可以㨂呢個職業。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n參考：afqhBODc_8U<br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n擋住啲怪嘅衝擊。<br />\n距離近嘅時候有長矛做輸出。<br />\n保護弓箭手同砲兵團，令佢哋有空間輸出。<br />\n攬皮帶，有啲咩事嘅時候後面嘅人可以拉你走。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n勇氣，唔驚怪。<br />\n信任後面嘅隊友，只要大家配合到，前線係唔會送到頭的。<br />\n注意做長矛兵嘅玩家要攞<span style=\"color: red;\">長盾</span>，啲怪好撞得，而且長矛兵陣做第一線係唔可以散的。<br />\n而長矛就係令到速狗怪冇得開衝刺技。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大浮板</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/VRvuH1G.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRvuH1G.png&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=c964ea00\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/VRvuH1G.png</a><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 抗怪物嘅近戰棍擊。<br />\n- 厚身嘅浮板應該可以喺一定距離之下擋到遠程火力，因為啲怪嘅火力唔係穿透屬性而係打擊屬性。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 唔ｃｕｍ打。<br />\n- 大嘅浮板可能會有啲貴。<br />\n- 要有合成技能。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大趴板</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/YVw9WYS.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYVw9WYS.png&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=12a87106\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/YVw9WYS.png</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">109蚊充氣板做盾牌,要成為前線標準裝備,一人一個<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dJAPtS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dJAPtS</a></span><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 抗怪物嘅近戰棍擊、蕉彈攻擊。<br />\n- 喺一定距離之下應該擋到遠程火力，因為啲怪嘅火力唔係穿透屬性而係打擊屬性。<br />\n- 應該唔使合成。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 可能唔ｃｕｍ打。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>環保紙皮</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/TA5ktBr.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTA5ktBr.png&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=70715234\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/TA5ktBr.png</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(守護香港) A字盾- 全民皆盾  簡易制作方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223329</a></span><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 平。<br />\n- 抗怪物嘅近戰棍擊。<br />\n- 厚身嘅紙皮應該可以喺一定距離之下擋到遠程火力，因為啲怪嘅火力唔係穿透屬性而係打擊屬性。<br />\n- 可以整定，可以入副本再整。<br />\n- 畀怪追，掉咗都唔肉赤。<br />\n- 我諗ＧＭ應該唔會紙皮都沒收啩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 真係要好多紙皮下。我整過八層冇Ａ字，用咗成個紙皮箱先整到一塊仔。<br />\n- 要同物資兵溝通下，派水嗰陣儘量沿住黏合位摵，唔好浪費紙皮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>山系女行Yama Girl</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/Y8f23aT.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8f23aT.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=9e4de38c\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/Y8f23aT.jpg</a> <br />\n優點：<br />\n- 平。<br />\n- 愈平愈好。<br />\n- 因為貴嘅係用鋁合金或者碳纖造，輕但係易爛。<br />\n- 前面個尖尖好似係用鎢金造，啫係最硬嘅金屬。<br />\n- 所以用嚟突刺係好過用嚟扑。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 有機會畀ＧＭ問候。<br />\n- 要收埋喺背囊嘅話，背囊要唔細。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>落雨不怕</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/oFW9Jeu.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFW9Jeu.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=c4ac53a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/oFW9Jeu.jpg</a> <br />\n優點：<br />\n- 落雨不怕。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 易爛。<br />\n- 長矛嚟講唔夠長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Thbd9Xs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThbd9Xs.png&h=19a33ab1&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>棍盾兵</strong></span></span><br />\n想同啲怪愈親愈熱，然後短兵相接嘅玩家，可以㨂呢個職業。<br />\n參考：veK-HDPzmww<br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n第一線體力不支嘅時候，畀佢哋向後退，然後近攻啲怪。<br />\n呢個時候啲怪就應該有啲攰㗎啦，不過你就應該有相對充裕嘅體力。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n喺未上前嘅時候，捉實第一線嘅皮帶，有咩事嘅時候將佢拉返向後面。<br />\n然後上前打怪，唔可以畀啲怪湧到入去後線。<br />\n可以攞細盾，有大啲嘅空間打怪。<br />\n以刺為主要攻擊，減少大幅度嘅身體動作，減少畀怪打嘅機會。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大浮板</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/VRvuH1G.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRvuH1G.png&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=c964ea00\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/VRvuH1G.png</a><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 抗怪物嘅近戰棍擊。<br />\n- 厚身嘅浮板應該可以喺一定距離之下擋到遠程火力，因為啲怪嘅火力唔係穿透屬性而係打擊屬性。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 唔ｃｕｍ打。<br />\n- 大嘅浮板可能會有啲貴。<br />\n- 要有合成技能。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>環保紙皮</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/TA5ktBr.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTA5ktBr.png&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=70715234\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/TA5ktBr.png</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(守護香港) A字盾- 全民皆盾  簡易制作方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223329</a></span><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 平。<br />\n- 抗怪物嘅近戰棍擊。<br />\n- 厚身嘅紙皮應該可以喺一定距離之下擋到遠程火力，因為啲怪嘅火力唔係穿透屬性而係打擊屬性。<br />\n- 可以整定，可以入副本再整。<br />\n- 畀怪追，掉咗都唔肉赤。<br />\n- 我諗ＧＭ應該唔會紙皮都沒收啩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 真係要好多紙皮下。我整過八層冇Ａ字，用咗成個紙皮箱先整到一塊仔。<br />\n- 要同物資兵溝通下，派水嗰陣儘量沿住黏合位摵，唔好浪費紙皮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>注意安全</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/bJ0bcJp.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJ0bcJp.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=41aba4ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/bJ0bcJp.jpg</a><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 唔使錢。<br />\n- 抗打擊，但唔知防唔防彈。<br />\n- 硬淨，材質係不少於三毫米嘅鋁合金板。<br />\n- 畀怪追，掉咗都唔肉赤。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 喺副本地圖入面執，要爬高爬低。<br />\n- 要自備手柄同工具，或者等工廠兵整好派街坊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>山系女行Yama Girl</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/Y8f23aT.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8f23aT.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=9e4de38c\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/Y8f23aT.jpg</a> <br />\n縮短嚟用。<br />\n優點：<br />\n- 平。<br />\n- 愈平愈好。<br />\n- 因為貴嘅係用鋁合金或者碳纖造，輕但係易爛。<br />\n- 前面個尖尖好似係用鎢金造，啫係最硬嘅金屬。<br />\n- 所以用嚟突刺係好過用嚟扑。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 有機會畀ＧＭ問候。<br />\n- 要收埋喺背囊嘅話，背囊要唔細。"},{"pid":"01d441e638bf4ca4620973a18c1e0e47cb080759","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YU80P0Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYU80P0Z.png&h=dc57ae0b&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>哨兵</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n將怪獸嘅情報通報畀咪手，同前線知。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n將情報通報畀ＴＧ谷，如果前線有戴smart watch 嘅話就可以好快咁收到消息。<br />\n用無線電將情報通告畀咪手知，因為唔係個個有戴錶，咁咪手就可以將情報帶畀前線。<br />\n注意同怪獸保持距離，以保安全。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>無線電</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/5WPWooJ.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WPWooJ.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=1d0324cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/5WPWooJ.jpg</a> <br />\n我諗唔使多講，請同咪手夾定頻道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8YN8YY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YN8YY3.png&h=e5fa1b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咪手／旗手</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n將情報客觀咁帶畀前線。<br />\n請記住唔係幫手做決定。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n用大聲公將情報講畀前線知。<br />\n請注意安全，咪手好有可能會變成怪獸針對嘅對象。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>無線電</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/5WPWooJ.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5WPWooJ.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=1d0324cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/5WPWooJ.jpg</a> <br />\n我諗唔使多講，請同哨兵夾定頻道。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大聲公</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/mkDW7Ug.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmkDW7Ug.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=a5f46e0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/mkDW7Ug.jpg</a> <br />\nIt is what it is."},{"pid":"73efcfb4c552c9d888c7615833eac81d84c444f6","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y1HwWQa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy1HwWQa.png&h=75232a36&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>工兵</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n喺副本地圖入面起有需要嘅Structures。<br />\n戰術性咁破壞副本地圖入面一開始就有嘅Structures（例如燈啊咁）。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n喺其他玩家掩護之下開建造技，小心唔好畀啲怪見到樣。<br />\n記得帶手套，唔好整親，同埋唔好留指紋。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n鉗、士巴拿、索帶<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔係六角匙呀 六角匙冇用架<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321717</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cvnjiB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cvnjiB.png&h=97fdaf28&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>工廠兵</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n幫手加工其他玩家要用嘅裝備，例如盾啊，護手啊咁。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n喺後線安全嘅位置做手作仔。<br />\n但係後線都唔一定代表安全，請小心怪獸包抄。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n唔同裝備嘅原材料（盾牌、盾柄，ｅｔｃ．）<br />\n索帶<br />\n封箱膠紙、Duct tape、較剪<br />\n電鑽、鏍絲"},{"pid":"833061855de0f655c095916a092526d973c9a1f1","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LnD0Qwn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnD0Qwn.png&h=ab003a84&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>急救員</strong></span></span><br />\n急救員係紅色，係因為我哋都知道啲怪會針住急救嚟打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n為有需要嘅玩家進行急救、洗眼、洗面等。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n有衛生常識同急救知識。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n我識得唔多，廢事誤導大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[721] 中椒急救大法, 包敷料有效減低痛楚. 集國際文獻、消防員、救護員實戰之大成<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335676</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香城Ｏｎｌｉｎｅ Ｗｉｋｉ藥品篇<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/18YJiHEvb6VBVidiaKvTiiqEr8IonNEnah5aWDbnWolE/edit#gid=197951424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F18YJiHEvb6VBVidiaKvTiiqEr8IonNEnah5aWDbnWolE%2Fedit%23gid%3D197951424&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=d1ebe056\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/18YJiHEvb6VBVidiaKvTiiqEr8IonNEnah5aWDbnWolE/edit#gid=197951424</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVJTq9L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVJTq9L.png&h=9f44cf39&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>滅火隊</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有咩做：<br />\n撲滅怪獸放出嚟嘅龍蛋攻擊。<br />\n要點做：<br />\n唔好驚龍蛋。<br />\n做好保護措施，有時即使覺得冇嘢，都唔一定冇受到傷害，耐咗先發覺舐嘢就太遲。<br />\n<br />\n裝備有：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">飯餸碟／蒸魚碟</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/191719_d303b5925d2630150e73cfc103774b8e.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F14%2F191719_d303b5925d2630150e73cfc103774b8e.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=fa961d61\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/14/191719_d303b5925d2630150e73cfc103774b8e.jpg</a><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 輕。<br />\n- 平。<br />\n- 可以疊埋，慳位。<br />\n- 唔使另外帶水。<br />\n- 可回收（不過會有味）。<br />\n- 放低走人，高機動性。<br />\n- 一個人搞掂。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 可能裝唔落大嘅龍蛋。<br />\n- 近距離。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雪糕筒</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/dJkFQFu.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJkFQFu.jpg&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=799d7276\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/dJkFQFu.jpg</a><br />\n優點：<br />\n- 唔使錢。<br />\n- 幾大嘅龍蛋都裝得落。<br />\n- 打完副本就掉，乾手淨腳。<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 要另外帶水。<br />\n- 滅火時間比較耐。<br />\n- 要幾個人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其他</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">[香城online攻略] 滅火攻略update<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430370</a></span>"},{"pid":"eac5949c9f21124ff386441382aac84497f10b81","tid":1503024,"uid":312492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:39:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1502375/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1502375/page/1</a><br />\n整ABS板盾牌分享<br />\n借位推俾啲唔夠Gear嘅手足睇"},{"pid":"b9da7ad2e20883d44b35502aa92e45d6c1e95985","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:39:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">戰術篇</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小弟建議嘅戰術係一個方陣戰術（夾心餅陣）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c88cU1P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc88cU1P.png&h=6da7f2ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺上面第一排嘅係鐵馬陣，主要係用嚟防彈。如果喺第一輪交火嘅時候，近戰玩家蹲低嘅話（蹲到同個盾一樣高，所以要長盾），怪獸開遠技嘅命中率自然唔高。<br />\n同埋速狗怪冇得用衝刺技。<br />\n<br />\n然後嘅係第一線嘅長矛兵，喺position 嘅時候將長矛隊向前，以突刺技能為主要攻擊。<br />\n第二三排嘅係棍盾手，未打怪嘅時候將棍收喺身，易攞出嚟嘅位。空出嚟嘅手就用嚟捉住前排嘅隊友。第三排嘅亦如是。如果同時間多人打副本嘅話，就可以排多幾行緃深。<br />\n棍盾手可以用圓盾嘅原因係，一嚟可以有更多嘅空間嚟打怪，二嚟就係當棍盾手同怪獸短兵相接嘅時候，相信怪獸係唔會寧願ＴＫ都要開槍嘅（相信隻ＧＡＭＥ嘅ＡＩ冇咁痴線）。<br />\n<br />\n隔一啲距離之後，就有我哋嘅弓箭手同砲兵團。<br />\n喺同怪獸對恃嘅時候，呢兩個職業嘅玩家就可以用曲射壓制對手。<br />\n喺呢個情況下，怪獸一係就撤退，一係就硬住頭皮衝前，咁嘅話頭排嘅玩家就會用長矛攔截怪獸。<br />\n所以弓箭手玩家係高輸出同埋相對安全嘅職業。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個位置嘅仲有咪手同工廠兵（我認為呢個係一個相對安全嘅位置，雖然行軍嘅時候唔係幾方便開工，所以做工廠兵嘅玩家可以兼任弓箭手、砲兵團，ｅｔｃ）<br />\n<br />\n後排嘅係一個鏡像嘅近戰玩家團，一個預備軍團。<br />\n當前面軍團交火之間有空間，而前面軍團狀態有疲累嘅時候，請同前面軍團（成個軍團）換人，以保持士氣同狀態高昂。<br />\n換人嘅時候，預備軍團行外圍，疲累嘅士兵行入面，以防止喺換人嘅時候畀野怪打到殘血嘅玩家。<br />\n<br />\n最後就係，我畫嘅呢個圖入面都只係得五十幾人，有玩過香城Ｏｎｌｉｎｅ嘅玩家都知道每次打副本都唔只咁少人。實際上嚟講：<br />\n１。弓箭手應該愈多愈好，甚至同近戰兵一樣咁多人都冇問題。一粒波子唔會有傷害，但係一次射五十粒就會有。<br />\n<br />\n２。縱深（近戰有幾多排）係愈多愈好，四至五排可以話係基本。但係記得陣型係好重要，唔好堆埋一舊咁。"},{"pid":"1fbada4761bfdcd0d8186cec557bef62685290fb","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:41:26.000Z","msg":"個目錄已經亂咗，大家唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ec4dbf12f2f3e0b86a1f890f56ea70ea62c852","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:42:17.000Z","msg":"深夜十連<br />\n１"},{"pid":"e0c3b5af710a9c5530cec626533ef853ad53913f","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:42:27.000Z","msg":"２"},{"pid":"cfb18db5d20be21e6ca18dd8d3d06d77ed1fc926","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:42:37.000Z","msg":"３"},{"pid":"a8f8d63600b5ccf8174f508a264801d450985353","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:42:47.000Z","msg":"４"},{"pid":"b90e215bdf56e82602f119a8ecd21a4538c15258","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:42:57.000Z","msg":"５"},{"pid":"8f77d7029c87c703bdd4a0a64da5871bd81e6580","tid":1503024,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:43:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反擊 還拖 打狗 救人</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d309f482abb272297c58e979b0caaec56bd09478","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:43:07.000Z","msg":"６"},{"pid":"7c05713abbef1fef271afd5146052195e89e54de","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:43:17.000Z","msg":"７"},{"pid":"f74a85b495b33519d8aff1f60827054118c858ba","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:43:35.000Z","msg":"再嚟過<br />\n１"},{"pid":"0e6a00693872635c16bfdc44aff95db9155acad8","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:43:45.000Z","msg":"２"},{"pid":"111cb8f4e405b77609d262d3d456a4f9ae65f1ea","tid":1503024,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T19:43:56.000Z","msg":"３"},{"pid":"4133dca2e